<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex">
    <title>Đang chờ vào hàng - movieCC</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .bg-gradient {
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 80%, rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }
        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 480px;
            padding: 48px 36px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-radius: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        .queue-icon {
            width: 88px;
            height: 88px;
            margin: 0 auto 24px;
            background: rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .queue-icon svg { color: #F4ABB4; }
        .queue-icon::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.25);
            border-top-color: #F4ABB4;
            animation: spin 1.5s linear infinite;
        }
        @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .desc {
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            color: #a0a0a0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 28px;
        }
        .stat-box {
            background: rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.15);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            color: #999;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
        .stat-value {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #F4ABB4;
            font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
        }
        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 14px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }
        .progress-fill {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            height: 100%;
            width: 30%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F4ABB4, #FED3DD);
            border-radius: 4px;
            animation: slide 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes slide {
            0%   { left: -30%; }
            100% { left: 100%; }
        }
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F4ABB4, #FED3DD);
            color: #1a1a1a;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .btn-ghost {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            color: #ccc;
        }
        .btn-ghost:hover {
            background: rgba(244, 171, 180, 0.08);
            color: #F4ABB4;
        }
        .tip {
            margin-top: 22px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-gradient"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="queue-icon">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Đang xếp hàng vào xem</h1>
        <p class="desc">
            Hiện có quá nhiều người xem cùng lúc. Bạn đang trong hàng đợi —
            trang sẽ tự động tải lại sau vài giây để giành chỗ kế tiếp.
        </p>
        <div class="stat-box">
            <div class="stat-label">Tự tải lại sau</div>
            <div class="stat-value" id="countdown">5s</div>
            <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill"></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="btn btn-primary">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2">
                    <polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/>
                    <path d="M20.49 15a9 9 0 1 1-2.12-9.36L23 10"/>
                </svg>
                Thử lại ngay
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
                    <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
                </svg>
                Trang chủ
            </a>
        </div>
        <p class="tip">Thông thường thời gian chờ dưới 10 giây. Cảm ơn bạn đã kiên nhẫn ❤</p>
    </div>
    <script>
        var n = 5;
        var el = document.getElementById('countdown');
        var t = setInterval(function() {
            n--;
            if (n <= 0) {
                clearInterval(t);
                location.reload();
                return;
            }
            el.textContent = n + 's';
        }, 1000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
